# Replace Your Video Team With AI - Content Series

**Goal:** Drive VideoMind AI customers through targeted LinkedIn/X content
**Strategy:** 170 posts targeting specific industries/roles  
**Format:** "Replace Your [X] Video Team With AI" hook + VideoMind solution

## Post Template

```
Replace Your [INDUSTRY] Video Team With AI

[PAIN POINT] is killing your [METRIC]. 

Most [INDUSTRY] companies waste:
• $X on video editors
• Y hours per project
• Z% of content never published

VideoMind AI changes this:
→ Any video becomes training data in minutes
→ Automated transcripts + summaries
→ Ready-to-use Q&A pairs for models

[SPECIFIC INDUSTRY BENEFIT]

Try it free: videomind-ai.com
```

